        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Remove legacy suspicious filtering and scanner rollups",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- removes the legacy suspicious visibility/filtering model (`isSuspicious`, suspicious flags, non-suspicious search/list params, non-suspicious leaderboard/index paths, CLI suspicious install prompts)\n- makes `/security-audit` top-level Outcome render canonical ClawScan verdict/state directly; VirusTotal and static analysis stay supporting telemetry only\n- keeps `clean`, `review`, and `warn` visible/installable; only ClawScan `malicious`, manual moderation blocks, or unrelated availability gates block access\n- updates docs/OpenAPI/schema/client tests and local seed fixtures to match the new model\n\n## Rollout / Merge Order\n\nThis PR is stacked on #2354 and must merge/deploy only after PR 1 has deployed and its cleanup/backfill has been verified.\n\nBefore merging this PR:\n\n1. Merge and deploy #2354.\n2. Run the PR 1 cursor-based backfills/cleanup in production:\n   - `maintenance:backfillSkillVersionClawScanFields`\n   - `maintenance:backfillPackageReleaseClawScanFields`\n   - `maintenance:cleanupLegacySuspiciousSkillFields`\n   - `maintenance:cleanupLegacySuspiciousDigestFields`\n   - `maintenance:cleanupLegacySuspiciousPackageScanStatuses`\n   - `maintenance:cleanupLegacySuspiciousPackageReleaseScanStatuses`\n3. Verify production data is clean enough for this schema/index narrowing:\n   - no `skills.isSuspicious` / `skillSearchDigest.isSuspicious` fields remain\n   - no `skills.moderationVerdict = \"suspicious\"` remains\n   - no `flagged.review` / `flagged.suspicious` moderation flags remain\n   - canonical `clawScanVerdict` / `clawScanState` are populated for relevant current skill versions and package releases\n   - package/package-release scan-status fields no longer contain legacy `suspicious`\n4. Deploy this PR. If rollback is needed after this PR, revert this PR and keep the PR 1 canonical verdict data.\n\n## Tests\n\n- `bunx vitest run convex/leaderboards.test.ts src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx src/routes/-dashboard.test.tsx src/components/artifacts/artifactStatus.test.ts --reporter=dot`\n- `bunx vitest run src/components/artifacts/artifactStatus.test.ts src/routes/-dashboard.test.tsx src/components/DetailSecuritySummary.test.tsx src/components/SkillSecurityScanResults.test.tsx --reporter=dot`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx tsc --noEmit`\n- `bun run ci:unit`\n- `bun run ci:static`\n- `bun run ci:types-build`\n- `bun run ci:packages`\n\n## Review Notes\n\n- `AUTOREVIEW_AUTO_TESTS=0 .agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --reviewer codex --fallback-reviewer none`\n- Accepted/fixed: stale OpenAPI moderation verdict enum and local seed fixture canonical fields.\n- Rejected by design: the schema narrowing warning is covered by the rollout gate above; PR 2 is intentionally not deployable until PR 1 cleanup/backfill verification passes.\n",
